<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div class="body"><iframe class="IsolatedDom-sc-h3zeen-0 kmHRJp"/><p class="reference" data-aid="154411349" id="reference1">&#x201C;September 16&#x2013;22: &#x2018;Lift Up Your Head and Be of Good Cheer.&#x2019; 3 Nephi 1&#x2013;7,&#x201D; <cite>Come, Follow Me&#x2014;For Home and Church: Book of Mormon 2024</cite> (2023)</p>
<p class="short-reference" data-aid="154411352" id="short_reference1">&#x201C;September 16&#x2013;22. 3 Nephi 1&#x2013;7,&#x201D; <cite>Come, Follow Me&#x2014;For Home and Church: 2024</cite> (2023)</p>
